Chris Marquette https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Marquette 0 Chris Marquette (born Christopher George Rodriguez; October 3, 1984) is an American film and television actor. He is known for his roles in such films as The Tic Code, Freddy vs. Jason, The Girl Next Door, Just Friends, Alpha Dog and Fanboys.
